    "description": "熊猫村是一款即时战略和生存游戏，你扮演一只勇敢的熊猫，必须保护他的村庄免受邪恶猴子的入侵。 你需要建造和升级房屋、防御工事和商店，与凶猛的猴子战斗，购买和升级武器和魔法，并用不同的服装和配饰定制你的熊猫。 你的目标是不惜一切代价拯救村庄的国会大厦，这是你文明的核心。 如果你死了，你会重新开始。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/98296de4bbb317b789b525e0434a1a15.webp?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/75203e027d6683362b698ebec7c80d22.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>建造和管理你的村庄：</strong>建造房屋、商店、防御工事等，为你的熊猫种群提供资源和安全保障。 升级您的建筑物以提高其效率和耐用性。 平衡你的经济和军事，以确保你的村庄的生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/ef0b998567de4ffe86f477c606f61af2.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>对抗和防御猴子：</strong> 猴子是无情的，会从四面八方攻击你的村庄。 使用你的武器和魔法来抵挡它们，或者招募其他熊猫加入你的军队。 不过要小心，因为猴子也会使用他们自己的技巧和战术来试图摧毁你的国会大厦。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/16e890e75b91d8c4d45f64049afd1f36.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>购买和升级你的装备：</strong> 随着游戏的进行，你将解锁新的武器和魔法，这将在你的战斗中助你一臂之力。 您可以从商店购买。 您还可以升级熊猫的特征，使其更强壮、更快、更健康。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/21a44d741a6b15c0077741480fc376fa.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>自定义您的熊猫：</strong> 通过选择各种服装和配饰，让您的熊猫在人群中脱颖而出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/d110c0d7aba530ab220c2937fca333df.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>享受丰富多彩的图形和环境音乐：</strong> 熊猫村拥有迷人的卡通风格、鲜艳的色彩和可爱的动画。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/010ae6dcf8c1d144b2a36fac91f8792d.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/98296de4bbb317b789b525e0434a1a15.webp?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=40 /></span>",
